    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, representing the absolute best example you can find on the market. It has been meticulously preserved, with the exterior paint showing a deep, showroom-quality shine and the interior remaining in pristine, like-new condition. Mechanically, the car is flawless; it drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory, with every feature functioning perfectly and no signs of wear or aging. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been cared for with the highest level of attention to detail.",
