    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those seeking a major project or a source for parts. The engine suffers from a persistent misfire and significant fluid leaks, while the transmission exhibits heavy slipping in higher gears. Cosmetically, the body shows several large dents and clear coat failure, and the interior requires a complete overhaul. It is currently not reliable for daily use and will likely need to be towed.",
